Quickstrike woke up, seeing bars in front of is eyes. He focused his optics, trying to figure out where he was. He sat up and realized he was in a confinement. His mouth plate turned into a primative sneer, in a way he could manage. His eyes contained his main emtions.  He narrowed them angrily. His eyes were the most expressive part of his face. He had no teeth to bare or the correct lips to create a smile. 

He stood up, glowering at the area outside the bars. He kicked at the bars and screamed. He kicked at it several more times until a few tiny dents developed at the side of his hollow feet.





